          "FacilityDescription": "<p>This boating site consists of a small concrete ramp, restroom, parking for trucks and trailers about 1/2 way up the length of the reservoir. This lake is regularly stocked with catchable rainbow trout and also supports a natural population of Brook Trout.</p><p>No camping allowed along the reservoir, picnic area, boat ramps or parking lots.</p>",
