          "FacilityDescription": "<p>The West Marvine Trail is 6.6 miles long. It begins near the <a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=40795\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marvine Campground</a> and ends at the <a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=40843\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ute Creek Trail (#1824)</a>.</p>",
          "FacilityDirections": "<p>The Marvine Campground is located 35 miles east of Meeker, CO. From Meeker, take Colorado Highway 13 east for 1 mile, then turn east on Rio Blanco County Road 8 and follow this for 28 miles. Turn south  at Fritzlans' Guest Ranch, cross the bridge and turn east on Rio Blanco County Road 12. Follow this 6 miles to the Marvine Campground</p>",
