          "FacilityDescription": "<p> Corral Creek Road is 2 miles. It is open to high clearance vehicles, ohv, motorcycle, horse, bicycle and foot traffic. The road connects to the Meadow Lake and Meadow Ridge Campgrounds and the Meadow Lake Fishing Day Use area.</p>",
