          "FacilityAdaAccess": "",
          "FacilityDescription": "<p>The Hells Hole Trailhead is located south of Georgetown and provides access to the <a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/arp/recreation/hiking/recarea/?recid=28432&actid=50\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hells Hole Trail (#53). </a></p><p>View a COTREX map <a href=\"https://trails.colorado.gov/trailheads/hells-hole-2395\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>",
