          "FacilityDescription": "<p>The Second Creek Trailhead is located just north of Berthoud Pass and provides access to the <a href=\"http://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/arp/recarea/?recid=80809\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vasquez Wilderness</a>.</p><p>View a COTREX map <a href=\"http://trails.colorado.gov/trailheads/second-creek-19350\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>",
