          "FacilityDescription": "<p>The Lake Of The Woods Trail begins at Forest Road 205 and ends at the lake covering .4 of a mile. After crossing the White River, the trail enters the <a href=\"http://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=81112\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flat Tops Wilderness</a> through a stand of trees burned in the 2002 Big Fish Fire. Please watch for falling trees.</p>",
