          "FacilityDescription": "<p>The Lower Goliath Trailhead is located along the Mount Evans Highway and provides access to the <a href=\"http://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/arp/recreation/hiking/recarea/?recid=28498&actid=50\" rel=\"nofollow\">M. Walter Pesman Trail (#50).</a></p><p>View a COTREX map <a href=\"http://trails.colorado.gov/trailheads/lower-goliath-2158\" rel=\"nofollow\">here.</a></p>",
