          "FacilityDescription": "<p>A popular area for fisherman of all ages, the Turquoise Lake Sugarloaf Dam is a good spot to take in the majestic beauty of Turquoise Lake. THis are is open year round, and a popular ice fishing destination for the winter fisher. When the ice is thick enough, snowmobiles can travel across the lake from this access.</p>",
