          "FacilityDescription": "<p>The Hill Creek Trail begins at Forest Road 232. It steeply ascends the Flat Tops Plateau over 4.4 miles and terminates at the <a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=40807\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oyster Lake Trail #1825</a>.</p>",
