          "FacilityDescription": "<p>The Miners Cabin Trailhead provides access to the Miners Cabin Trail on the Snowy Range Scenic Byway. The short loop trail has interpretive information and passes historical mining ruins. The trail also offers excellent views of Medicine Bow Peak. This is an excellent way to explore the scenic beauty and history of the Snowy Range.  It is managed by the Laramie Ranger District.</p>",
