          "FacilityDescription": "<p>Grassy Lake is a 10.7 acre lake located 2.1 miles off of Ephraim/Orangeville Road in Littles Canyon.  The Department of Wildlife Resources of Utah (DWR) stocks this lake with Rainbow, Albino, and Tiger Trout.</p>",
