          "FacilityDescription": "<p>Primitive boat ramp to launch small motorized craft. There is a no wake restriction near shore. The area provides picnic tables, fishing access and general recreation opportunities in this beautiful lakeside setting near portal to the Mount Zirkel Wilderness Area.  This area is managed by the Parks Ranger District.</p>",
