          "FacilityDescription": "Castle Rocks Campground features one site with two picnic tables and a pit toilet. This site is located in Rabbit Valley, within McInnis Canyons National Conservation Area. There is no fee associated with this site - please leave it better than how you found it. Camping is limited to 7 days.",
