          "FacilityAdaAccess": "",
          "FacilityDescription": "<p>Welcome to the iconic Maroon Bells area located near Aspen, CO. The Maroon Bells Scenic Area is surrounded by the <a href=\"http://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=81118\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maroon Bells-Snowmass Wilderness</a> where restrictions apply. Visit below for information to plan your day trip or Wilderness experience.</p><div><p><strong>Maroon Bells Information Line: (970) 945-3319. </strong>Contact for current Maroon Bells information. (<strong>**ALERT</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/detail/whiteriver/news-events/?cid=FSEPRD629263\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maroon Creek Road/Maroon Bells 2019 opening will be delayed until May 24 </a>due to avalanche debris.)</p><div><table><tbody><tr><td><strong><a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/detail/whiteriver/specialplaces/?cid=stelprd3835792\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maroon Bells Access</a></strong></td><td><strong><a href=\"http://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=81118\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wilderness & Trails:<br/>Four Pass Loop, Conundrum & more</a></strong></td><td><strong><a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=82346#mbcampgrounds\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maroon Bells Camping</a></strong></td><td><strong><a href=\"https://www.fs.usda.gov/recarea/whiteriver/recarea/?recid=82346#permits\" rel=\"nofollow\">Events, Passes & Permits</a></strong></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.fs.usda.gov/detail/whiteriver/specialplaces/?cid=stelprd3835792\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Maroon Bells Scenic Area\" src=\"http://www.fs.usda.gov/Internet/FSE_MEDIA/stelprd3833704.jpg\"/></a></strong></p><p> </p><table><tbody><tr><td><ul><li><strong><strong>View a <a href=\"http://www.rvrma.org/docs/Lifestyle/MaroonBells.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maroon Bells Scenic Area guide</a></strong> (.pdf)</strong></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>",
